      "text": "みなさーん、明けましておめでとうございまーす！\nサニーピースの川咲さくらでーす！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello‚ everyone! Happy New Year!\nI'm Sakura Kawasaki from Sunny Peace!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.4,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
