    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "お待たせしました！\nすみません、着替えるのに時間がかかっちゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry for the wait!\nI took a bit longer to change‚ I'm sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.3000001001,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 27.8666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに焦らなくても大丈夫だ\n次の仕事まで、まだ時間に余裕はあるからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's no need to rush that much.\nWe still have time until the next job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "これからテレビ局に移動ですよね？\nそこでバラエティ番組の生放送に出て……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're heading to the TV station now‚ right?\nThere‚ we'll do a live broadcast for a variety show…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_01-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "それからライブのリハーサルがあって\n夕方にラジオの収録……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and then we have a rehearsal for the live\nfollowed by a radio recording in the late afternoon…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.3728913249,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "年末からハードスケジュールが続いているが\n体調は大丈夫か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The schedule has been pretty tough since the end of the year‚\nbut…are you feeling okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_01-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "私は元気一杯です！\nもっとお仕事を増やしても平気ですよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm full of energy!\nI can handle even more work!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_01-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "今のサニピには勢いがありますから\nこの勢いに乗っていろんなことに挑戦してみたいです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sunny Peace is on fire right now‚\nso I want to challenge myself to many things!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_05_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "挑戦といえば\nさくらに新しい仕事のオファーがきていたな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Speaking of challenges…\nThere was a new job offer for you‚ Sakura.",
        "id": ""
      },
